{"tid":433050,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"有無人同我一樣鐘意做木工？","createTime":"2017-10-12T05:15:51.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-15T06:33:52.000Z","uid":121877,"like":21,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"2e010d6a2e1740da0f3e406679c7476f08749864","tid":433050,"uid":121877,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-12T05:15:51.000Z","msg":"小弟今年岩岩畢業，就狠下心腸全職走左去鬥木（其實讀緊書個時已經開始做緊，不經不覺原來已經接近３年），向觀塘海濱個邊租左間細細哋嘅工場，如果CHING、C姐有興趣可以上來參觀下或者一齊鬥下木，多多指教！<br />\n<br />\n其實我主要造細件野多，好似木筆、木戒指、木手鐲、木筷子、木餐具等等。<br />\n<br />\n木筆就有分鉛芯、粗幼原子筆、粗幼鋼筆、直斜桿筆、毛筆等。<br />\n其實封端式係指成枝筆既外形一體成形，都係木。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/10/12/125447_34d25193acc15a8f20b70ce8f9daf43e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F10%2F12%2F125447_34d25193acc15a8f20b70ce8f9daf43e.jpg&h=86f253d8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/10/12/124426_156005c5baf40ff51a327f1c34f2975b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F10%2F12%2F124426_156005c5baf40ff51a327f1c34f2975b.jpg&h=d5fe2813&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n木筆係比較受歡迎嘅木作，應該係因為佢實用性比較高？<br />\n<br />\n木戒指就有好多人上來整都幾有特色嘅造型 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ...<br />\n但係我又好矛盾咁覺得圓形真係好難整 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/10/12/124908_d0096ec6c83575373e3a21d129ff8fef.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F10%2F12%2F124908_d0096ec6c83575373e3a21d129ff8fef.jpg&h=66699256&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n木手鐲除左整外型，得閒個陣會整下小鑲嵌（真係唔係就咁拎膠水痴咁流&hellip;）<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/10/12/125519_065e47fe7169ad4f50aadeda3a359359.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F10%2F12%2F125519_065e47fe7169ad4f50aadeda3a359359.jpg&h=3026aa80&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n呢對係用手刻嘅金石紋楠木筷子，整完咁上左層薄薄地嘅生漆。<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/10/12/125559_0c0525957da2e84364743353e15119ec.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F10%2F12%2F125559_0c0525957da2e84364743353e15119ec.jpg&h=ff6ec13b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n不過，我最喜歡都係雕刻，有創作先至有多點趣！<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/10/12/125943_79814c216eee6d3a8c562ecab385d7b9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F10%2F12%2F125943_79814c216eee6d3a8c562ecab385d7b9.jpg&h=03a7422e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n我嘅工作室係：<br />\n白犬工坊　木工布藝工作坊<br />\n工作室見到的，都能買，都能學造，歡迎到來參觀！<br />\n觀塘海濱道139-141號海濱中心9樓907室<br />\n聯絡電話：98614994 （可whatsapp）<br />\n營業時間：1030-2230 （敬請預約）"},{"pid":"534d28f0db60c3ef493e9341f8e1f4813c0fb618","tid":433050,"uid":10788,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-12T05:19:54.000Z","msg":"正呀巴打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n小弟玩開皮 一路都想自己做工具 做工具架 做傢私<br />\n同做皮一樣 市面買永遠都無理想咁好<br />\n有諗過買部車床 可惜無位"},{"pid":"511f33c12845f92d717c5886b2c43fb9f5f2d4b7","tid":433050,"uid":3164,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-12T05:21:30.000Z","msg":"啲作品幾靚！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6778db8e86a4e1d2e7843a04d81db6f668e40a62","tid":433050,"uid":10788,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-12T05:22:37.000Z","msg":"有機會想上黎參觀下 太正了<br />\n有無興趣交換技能<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nBtw 巴打點睇廿一由八"},{"pid":"aa477965237a309fe2742560248db5e5caf243bb","tid":433050,"uid":114275,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-12T05:28:15.000Z","msg":"有 !  鐘意做手作 但苦無工具同技術"},{"pid":"84ed542971d0c38e2d3ab649b05c63acec86851d","tid":433050,"uid":40908,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-12T05:34:34.000Z","msg":"有follow開你地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 不過少貴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"42827caebc308a1834e5077043ede7cb1c721c5e","tid":433050,"uid":121877,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-12T16:14:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>正呀巴打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n小弟玩開皮 一路都想自己做工具 做工具架 做傢私<br />\n同做皮一樣 市面買永遠都無理想咁好<br />\n有諗過買部車床 可惜無位</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我地好多枱枱凳凳都係自己整啊<br />\n比如呢一Set<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/10/13/001401_cca00c5ebf1a41ea6ebfa4dbddf5905a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F10%2F13%2F001401_cca00c5ebf1a41ea6ebfa4dbddf5905a.jpg&h=46c38de6&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"8b73553977d703e0ea7160da943ac70904006b9e","tid":433050,"uid":60169,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-12T17:53:26.000Z","msg":"屌你jp"},{"pid":"0aa7f5c59c29a400549cd86ab31292b9ce95f781","tid":433050,"uid":60169,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-12T17:53:49.000Z","msg":"屌你老母， 賣廣告死開啲"},{"pid":"a32ccfaacdaafa2ad2652fd468f5843db842f2c9","tid":433050,"uid":97267,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-12T18:57:53.000Z","msg":"有咩方法可以接觸/長學?"},{"pid":"d6c9c8e878b254f10dce317bb8914f2a977c13bf","tid":433050,"uid":112907,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-12T19:00:54.000Z","msg":"請唔請人？"},{"pid":"f85e6f4525c20409967b25ab84eda7633e05c0fc","tid":433050,"uid":121877,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-15T06:19:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>請唔請人？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n未有能力請人..<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d26ca16a5473db58317c2580b320ee419f33bf39","tid":433050,"uid":53172,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"ci